<div align="left" style="margin:23px 0px 0 0;width:980px;padding: 0 0 0 0px;" id="whoweare">
<h2 style="font-size:1.5em;" class="top">Who We Are</h2>
<p style="margin: 0px;font-size:1.10em;color:#444466;line-height:1.35em;" align="justify">Heat and Control is one of the world's leading manufacturers of food processing, seasoning, conveying, packaging and inspection equipment systems. We have over 65 years experience, 211 U.S. patents, and the best staff of engineers, technicians and consultants in the industry. Our mixture of know-how, innovation and commitment to quality guarantees best-of-breed custom solutions to any part of your production.<img src="images/spacer.gif" width="55" height="1" border="0"><a href="aboutus.asp" class="bluenav" style="font-weight:bold;font-size:.9em;">...More about Heat and Control</a><img src="topimages/redarrow.gif" width="8" height="8" align="absmiddle" style="margin-left:3px;"> </p>
</div>
<div align="center" style="width:1080px;margin-top:38px;"><div style="width:530px;float:left;margin-left:17px;" align="left">
